/>\n但坐佢附近既就真係多撚謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3921cf935edb49419e7c0b251f7dddd34e0b3d30","tid":262974,"uid":113165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b8d2f598e55b41225dd5d2a77a39d06e5d79e5","tid":262974,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"腳短細路頂住張登成撚日<br />\n屌佢老母通常都一句小朋友係咁嫁啦"},{"pid":"8f9d31d3e70adba95f02789ab2bba17021ad77f0","tid":262974,"uid":34132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶得個細路出街，就要確保個細路嘅安全同為佢哋嘅一切行為負責，大人同小朋友冇一個係無辜，只有唔識教嘅大人同唔受教嘅𡃁仔。<br />\n<br />\n出街又好撘飛機都好，帶住個細路俾人屌的話唔好同人講：&quot;唉，啲細路仔係咁架喇，由得佢啦&quot;<br />\n你要記住係你同你個廢柴老公/婆嘅無能導致週圍嘅人不便，你道撚完歉之後唯一可以做嘅就係用任何方法令你同另外件廢柴必出嚟嘅廢物收斂啲。</blockquote><br />\n講得好撚柒岩"},{"pid":"945e490fcb323aa08625989b7a5e2fd57226c987","tid":262974,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"坐經濟艙預撚咗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705b01a8267c4541ad4fbb398c6ec8da1dcf3b6","tid":262974,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐經濟艙預撚咗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來仲諗住#7係全lihkg最廢既回覆"}]}